  "body": "### Description\n\nIntegrate the Vale linter into Quarkus docs PRs to increase doc quality and style consistency by using a GitHub action that:\r\n- Analyzes the diff only.\r\n- Reports style errors, warnings, and suggestions in-line.\r\n- Does not block the PR from being merged if errors, warnings, or suggestions exist. \r\n- Uses the Quarkus Style vale rules, as defined in https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/docs/.vale/vale.ini\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n[Relates to https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/28584, which integrates Vale much earlier in the git workflow for the docs]",
